264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T16:18:22.000Z","msg":"擺渡人<br />\n有人話好爛<br />\n但係我又覺得題材幾新穎<br />\n同埋帶出意義幾好<br />\nbtw有部分係為左朝偉同eason<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272072efd53bbb3830064d725b99c029bca93078","tid":59234,"uid":40337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T16:22:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>踏血尋梅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學到啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f28e1dd48be7881dff7d8de55be1db575da00cb","tid":59234,"uid":54812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T16:27:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>secret life of Walter Mitty<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同好"},{"pid":"ab85ed7a097c797583fbc5706b0bc3877a777d1d","tid":59234,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T16:33:03.000Z","msg":"最近嗰套collateral beauty <br />\n<br />\n究竟愛 時間 死 係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded895d9b19204a356ae66fd7f205911b46c0bfd","tid":59234,"uid":17421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T16:53:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>secret life of Walter Mitty<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n&quot;To see the world, things dangerous to come to, to see behind walls, draw closer, to find each other, and to feel. That is the purpose of life.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n呢一套戲由出trailer時已經好hyped，好想入戲院睇，睇到最後仲眼濕濕。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能係太已代入呢一種無聊嘅生活，好似一隻已經習慣喺寵入面生活嘅雀意外飛出寵外咁。<br />\n<br />\n每一年都會喺聖誕嗰排重溫（iTunes買咗），令自己慢慢摸返對生命嘅期待、冒險嘅勇氣、求知嘅動力同重新感受與人相處嘅喜怒哀樂。<br />\n<br />\nSean O'Connell嗰句&quot;Beautiful things don't ask for attention&quot;與「君子病無能焉，不病人之不己知也」好相似，可以從中思考下Walter嘅處世之道。<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係最好睇，但係係一套好meaningful+靚嘅電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36f7d9f15a9920e1862ffd65e58799e08987742","tid":59234,"uid":54812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T17:02:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>secret life of Walter Mitty<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n&quot;To see the world, things dangerous to come to, to see behind walls, draw closer, to find each other, and to feel. That is the purpose of life.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n呢一套戲由出trailer時已經好hyped，好想入戲院睇，睇到最後仲眼濕濕。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能係太已代入呢一種無聊嘅生活，好似一隻已經習慣喺寵入面生活嘅雀意外飛出寵外咁。<br />\n<br />\n每一年都會喺聖誕嗰排重溫（iTunes買咗），令自己慢慢摸返對生命嘅期待、冒險嘅勇氣、求知嘅動力同重新感受與人相處嘅喜怒哀樂。<br />\n<br />\nSean O'Connell嗰句&quot;Beautiful things don't ask for attention&quot;與「君子病無